data.value: I'm a freelance developer based in Tacloban City, Philippines, specialising in building vb.net apps & web, consider myself Mid Level Full-stack developer but I tend to work more on the front-end. I also enjoy making apps in .net and tweaking with web apps in my spare time. I like .net, sql, html, css, js, php, and Linux. I enjoy building stuff, investigating new technologies and general hacking. I tend to follow start-ups scene and game server developers. If there's a livestream in my facebook page you may see me there.
